Package: PubMatrixR
Version: 2.0
Title: Search Entrez Using Boolean AND Queries
Author: Tyler Laird [aut, cre], Toledo Enrique [ctb]
Maintainer: Toledo Enrique <enriquetoledo@gmail.com>
Authors@R: c(person("Tyler", "Laird", email = "tylerscottlaird@gmail.com",
    role = "aut"),
    person("Toledo", "Enrique", email = "enriquetoledo@gmail.com", role = c("ctb", "cre")))
Description: Search two lists against each other on PubMed and obtain a resulting pairwise matrix. This package performs systematic literature searches using Boolean AND queries and creates co-occurrence matrices showing publication counts for term combinations. 
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
